"landingFeatureTimerText": "Work in fixed intervals with focus phases, short breaks and long breaks. This keeps your focus planned and your workday better structured.",
"landingFeatureTasksTitle": "Task management for your work",
"landingFeatureTasksText": "Connect focus sessions with specific tasks. Later you can see more clearly where your focused work time was spent.",
"landingFeatureStatsTitle": "Productivity statistics with overview",
