"landingFaqOneQuestion": "Can I use Time2Focus without an account?",
"landingFaqOneAnswer": "Yes. You can use the timer directly in the browser. An account is useful if you want to sync data later and use it on multiple devices.",
"landingFaqTwoQuestion": "Is Time2Focus only a Pomodoro timer?",
"landingFaqTwoAnswer": "No. Time2Focus combines a Pomodoro timer, focus sessions, task management and statistics so you can connect work and progress more clearly.",
"landingFaqThreeQuestion": "Does Time2Focus work on smartphones?",
"landingFaqThreeAnswer": "Yes. The web app is responsive and can be used in the browser on desktop, tablet and smartphone.",
